# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
The algorithm traverse from the end upto 0. Initially we set the last index as our `goal` then if we can reach the goal from  `i`th index , then we set our goal index to `i`th index.
Eventually if goal reaches to `0` then we know we can reach the last index from starting point (`0`th index).
